title: FK 6726 Tulip Lounge Chair - Low Castors
body: Inspired by the 1964 design of Preben Frabricius & Jorgen Kastholm, this Mobelaris style FK 6726 Tulip Lounge Chair - Low Castors is a unique masterpiece. Manufactured with the highest quality stainless steel and a frame covered with a thick canvas material to support the sumptuous Premium Aniline cushions.
